dct_description_sm: Relief shown pictorially. The title cartouche includes branches of fruit and is topped with a vase of flowers and fruit. This state was published in atlases by Jan Jansson between 1631 and 1633. From the Jansson Appendix Atlas 1636-1680, title created to represent a unique collection within the Clark Library, University of Michigan. 1 map; 36 x 47 cm.
